   PHLUID EPIDEMIC by Sinned Soul & Protocol


        After half a year later, pHluid returns with a brand new 12.8 MB
  music disk.  Packed with more than an 1.5 hours of high-quality MOD music,
  it features new releases from Bibby, Kneko, kX^mode, Patientzero, Protocol,
  and SiN.  This disk also contains MC6 entries, including Piano Man's final
  track ever, his Music Contest 6 entry "Recall" (m6i-rcal.it).  You can
  download the full disk from http://phluid.acid.org.



